OL,3,CUkrainian prisoners offered release
OL,4,Cbut must join military in return
OL,6,FUkrainian prisoners have been offered
OL,7,Frelease only if they agree to "defend
OL,8,Fthe motherland" and join the fight
OL,9,Fagainst Russia.
OL,11,FFor the first time Ukraine is
OL,12,Fincluding its prison population in the
OL,13,Fmilitary draft to address manpower
OL,14,Fshortages, as Russia's military builds-
OL,15,Fup in the east and makes gradual gains
OL,16,Fin the west.
