OL,3,CUkrainian prisoners offered release
OL,4,Cbut must join military in return
OL,6,FA recruiter, a member of a volunteer
OL,7,Fassault battalion, told prisoners at a
OL,8,Frural penal colony in southeast
OL,9,FUkraine, that they could "start a new
OL,10,Flife" by joining the war.
OL,12,F"You can put an end to this and start
OL,13,Fa new life," they said.
OL,15,F"The main thing is your will, because
OL,16,Fyou are going to defend the
OL,17,Fmotherland. You won't succeed at 50%,
OL,18,Fyou have to give 100% of yourself,
OL,19,Feven 150%."
