OL,3,CUkrainian prisoners offered release
OL,4,Cbut must join military in return
OL,6,FDeputy Justice Minister Olena
OL,7,FVysotska, said: "A lot of the
OL,8,Fmotivation comes from (inmates)
OL,9,Fwanting to return home a hero, and not
OL,10,Fto return home from prison."
OL,12,FShe added the programme could provide
OL,13,Fas many as 5,000 recruits which would
OL,14,F"definitely help" Ukraine's war effort.
